<section id='Lower'>
<title>Lower</title>

<command>
<cmdsynopsis>
    <arg choice='plain'>Lower</arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</command>

<para>Allows the user to lower a window.  Note that this lowers a window
only in its layer.  To bring a window to the absolute bottom, use</para>

<programlisting>
<fvwmref cmd="AddToFunc"/> lower-to-bottom
 + I <fvwmref cmd="Layer"/> 0 0
 + I Lower
</programlisting>

</section>
